data.description: This one story home is the picture of comfort and coziness! As you enter the front door & foyer you find yourself in a spacious and inviting living room. The kitchen is adjacent to the living room & dining room. It also features 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, and includes a large primary ensuite. The outside features a nice deck perfect for enjoying the spacious backyard. This home is filled with warmth, comfort, and the promise of cherished memories for a fortunate family to call their own!
